from climate change,

00:49:26.010 --> 00:49:29.280
and what can consumers
and Google do

00:49:29.280 --> 00:49:31.982
to apply additional influence
and pressure on that front?

00:49:31.982 --> 00:49:33.440
KATHARINE WILKINSON:
So I'm sort of

00:49:33.440 --> 00:49:35.700
geeked out that this
would be an example I

00:49:35.700 --> 00:49:37.800
wanted to talk to you about.

00:49:37.800 --> 00:49:40.500
And you have their
carpet in this room.

00:49:40.500 --> 00:49:42.240
This is a company
called Interface.

00:49:46.530 --> 00:49:51.450
They're a public company,
but they're smallish.

00:49:51.450 --> 00:49:53.820
They're headquartered
in Georgia,

00:49:53.820 --> 00:49:56.910
and they have been an
absolute vanguard and pioneer

00:49:56.910 --> 00:49:59.910
in sustainability on business.

00:49:59.910 --> 00:50:04.590
Their late founder
and CEO actually read

00:50:04.590 --> 00:50:08.070
one of Paul's earlier books,
"The Ecology of Commerce",

00:50:08.070 --> 00:50:11.626
in the mid-90s and had
this sort of revelation of,

00:50:11.626 --> 00:50:13.500
we have been raping and
pillaging the planet,

00:50:13.500 --> 00:50:18.240
and someday titans of industry
who have acted like me

00:50:18.240 --> 00:50:19.980
are going to go to jail.

00:50:19.980 --> 00:50:22.112
And he set Interface
on a course-- they

00:50:22.112 --> 00:50:23.320
no idea how they would do it.

00:50:23.320 --> 00:50:26.610
It's a petrochemical-based
carpet manufacturing company--

00:50:26.610 --> 00:50:31.372
to get to zero environmental
footprint by 2020.

00:50:31.372 --> 00:50:32.580
It's been an amazing journey.

00:50:32.580 --> 00:50:36.120
And now you see companies
like Unilever saying,

00:50:36.120 --> 00:50:38.940
we're able to do what we're
doing because Interface

00:50:38.940 --> 00:50:43.350
opened up the space to do this
and showed the example that you

00:50:43.350 --> 00:50:46.800
can improve financial
performance at the same time

00:50:46.800 --> 00:50:50.960
as you're dramatically shifting
your environmental performance.

00:50:50.960 --> 00:50:54.660
So 2020 aspiration of
zero, mission zero,

00:50:54.660 --> 00:50:56.310
